collection.description:
inBetweeners is a global crowdsourced community focused on spreading love and positivity across the metaverse. Access to the community is limited to 10,777 bear holders, each special in its own way.

The art is hand drawn by GianPiero, a world-renowned artist whose work has been sought after by Snoop Dog, Netflix, Levis, Bel Aire Rose, and more.

For inBetweeners, GianPiero has joined up with Justin Bieber to bring the NFTs to the world stage. Behind them, is a team of start-up operators, celebrities, and growth marketers to ensure the longevity of the community.

The game takes place in a fantasy-themed island called Mavia, where players build bases on plots of land and battle neighboring bases and armies to earn in-game resources, such as Mavias P2E cryptocurrency RUBY. Players must strategically place defensive buildings on their base such as walls, turrets and traps, in order to defend against opportunistic attackers looking to steal resources. Resources can also be stolen from rival bases through attacking opponents with land troops, vehicle and air units. RUBY is earned through battling enemy armies, and can be used to upgrade Land, Statue and Hero NFTs.

detail.name: COMMON #5512
detail.description:
Land is the most valuable NFT asset type inside of the Mavia ecosystem. Land is required in order to build a base, train an army and attack rival bases in order to earn Gold, Oil and RUBY. Your Land NFT can be used to play the game, but can also be used to form a partnership with another player, or can simply be rented out to others for passive RUBY income via the Mavia marketplace.

All land types behave the same in the game, and there is no offensive or defensive advantage to having higher rarity base. Common Land is the most frequently found base type, and it makes up 70% of the land in Mavia. Common Land has the least amount of environment decorations, the most basic type of map location and also has no extra luck factor when removing obstacles.

Our goal is to attract imaginative Dreamers and Adventurers who are passionate about learning and growing in Web3. Each Boki grants you access to Boki's holder-only Discord channels, digital and IRL events, exclusive merch, and more.

To those who live with their heads in the clouds: welcome home. The World of Boki is home to anyone and everyone.
